{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, if you got-- meet somebody good, you want to-- he wants to be a friend of yours, you want to be a friend of him, so you-- so you associate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, there was laws, certain laws, against discrimination, which the-- [COUGHS] the government was passing laws.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So discrimination was a bad word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very bad to-- to call somebody, uh, you know, a dirty Jew, a dumb Polack, you know, like here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't have those things, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Unless if somebody said that, you know, which it happened to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A boy told me 'dirty Jew,' so I went to my boss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He took that to his office and he scolded him pretty good and so he remembered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, he said, 'next time, you know, I'm going to go to the police and you're going to wind up, you know, where you belong, if you don't behave like a human being.'",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was really encouraging.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was nice, you know, to be where you can feel-- you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't feel, as a Jew, you know, that I'm mistreated, or-- by a boss, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you're a good worker, they appreciate it, and they really-- if you were worth promoting, they give you a promotion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was-- it was really nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you didn't have no freedom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you said something, like my friends from Warsaw, [CLEARS THROAT] they came to-- to eat in that restaurant, the food, and they said the food is bad.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, it's so horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was the talk against the government, because everything was owned by the government.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
